These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, havana, blend, dannemann
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, rock-climbing, board-games, camping
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, bellflower, daffodil, azalea
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, juice, fanta
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4
 3. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is the blend-smoker##1
 8. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is camping##2
10. the bolivar-smoker is the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | blend  | bolivar    | dannemann    | havana   |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing     | photography   | board-games       | camping    |
| Flower   | bellflower | iris | azalea    | daffodil |
| Beverage           | cola | fanta       | hot-chocolate | juice     |

