.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
House: art-deco, tower, cottage, futuristic
4 different games are played: domino, monopoly, billiard, mah-jongg
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, dahlia, lily, begonia
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, sprite
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
 2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the cottage house##1
 4. the tower house is the person who growsbellflower##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
 7. the futuristic house is on the right of the cottage house##1
 8. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 9. the person who growslily is on the far left or far right##3
10. the cottage house is in an odd position##4
11. the person who growslily is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| House          | art-deco  | tower    | cottage     | futuristic       |
| Game         | billiard | mah-jongg | domino   | monopoly |
| Flower   | lily | bellflower   | dahlia   | begonia    |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | sprite  | almond-milk | hot-chocolate   |

