.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, cherry, radish, lemon
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, reading, filmmaking, hiking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, sunflower, dahlia, daffodil
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, bike, van, subway
 1. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 2. the person who growssunflower is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 5. the person eating cherry is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
 9. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is the person eating radish##1
11. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Food      | kiwi | radish   | lemon    | cherry      |
| Hobby           | filmmaking | traveling | reading | hiking     |
| Flower   | sunflower      | daffodil   | begonia   | dahlia |
| Transport           | subway         | snowmobile       | van  | bike       |

