The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, daffodil, amaryllis, orchid
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, jet-ski, snowmobile, motorbike
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is the futuristic house##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 3. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the tower house##3
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is the tower house##1
12. the tower house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | may       | september   | april   | february   |
| House       | art-deco        | tower | futuristic    | farmhouse       |
| Flower      | orchid | daffodil    | amaryllis  | tulip |
| Transport      | jet-ski  | snowmobile  | trike | motorbike    |

