.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, thai, japanese, british
House: townhouse, art-deco, cottage, colonial
City: san-francisco, venice, nizza, prague
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, pink, fuchsia, aquamarine
 1. the person who likes pink is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the cottage house is between the person who likes coral and the british##2
 3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 4. the person traveling to venice is the egyptian##1
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
 6. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
 7. the thai is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 8. the cottage house is the person traveling to venice##1
 9. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
10. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the colonial house##1
11. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the japanese##3
12. the colonial house is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Nationality    | japanese    | british      | egyptian          | thai    |
| House   | art-deco | colonial       | cottage | townhouse |
| City     | prague     | nizza      | venice     | san-francisco |
| Color   | pink   | aquamarine | fuchsia        | coral   |

