 3. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 4. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 8. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 9. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
10. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
12. the person who growsamaryllis is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
