.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-8::.
4 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, bridge, poker
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, designer, social-worker, pilot
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, boat, helicopter, bike
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, july, october, april
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the social-worker is in an odd position##4
 5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person driving the jet-ski and the designer##2
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
12. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person playing go##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Game         | mah-jongg  | bridge    | go    | poker |
| Job   | social-worker   | entrepreneur       | designer  | pilot    |
| Transport   | jet-ski | boat | helicopter | bike   |
| Birthday           | october    | february        | april   | july    |

