4 different games are played: snooker, domino, whist, canasta
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, musician, chef, security-guard
 1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 2. the chef is in an even position##4
 3. the person playing snooker is between the person who growszinnia and the musician##2
 4. the chef is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the person playing canasta is in an odd position##4
 8. the security-guard is the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
11. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person playing domino is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
13. the person playing whist is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
