 1. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating mango##1
 2. the person eating kale is between the person driving the van and the person watching epic movies##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person watching zombie movies is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person watching epic movies##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching epic movies##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food      | lemon   | kale   | asparagus     | mango   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | zombie       | epic | superhero |
| Birthday           | june     | august   | may     | november     |
| Transport         | van | airplane | bike   | helicopter |

