.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, gospel, disco, pop
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse, ferret, turtle
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, lily, balloon-flower, begonia
House: palace, ranch-style, cottage, futuristic
 1. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 2. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
 3. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 4. the person who growslily is in an even position##4
 5. the palace house is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
 9. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
10. the cottage house is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
11. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
12. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Music-Genre      | disco       | gospel | trance        | pop        |
| Pet         | turtle | ferret       | chinchilla | horse |
| Flower   | begonia     | lily        | marigold    | balloon-flower      |
| House         | ranch-style     | cottage    | futuristic | palace   |

