.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, snake, frog
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, videographer, photographer, fisherman
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, davidoff, havana, chaman
There 4 different types of food: radish, apricot, carrot, artichoke
 1. the owner of the frog is the havana-smoker##1
 2. the havana-smoker is between the engineer and the fisherman##2
 3. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 4. the person eating apricot is on the left of the videographer##1
 5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 6. the owner of the bird is the davidoff-smoker##1
 7. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
 8. the fisherman is in an even position##4
 9. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
10. the engineer is in an even position##4
11. the engineer is on the far right##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet   | bird      | guinea-pig | frog     | snake        |
| Job   | photographer | fisherman  | videographer     | engineer |
| Cigar         | davidoff    | bluemaster | havana      | chaman |
| Food     | artichoke | apricot     | carrot | radish       |

 